`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Immtalk
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * immtalk <message>
 * immtalk

 Immtalk sends a message to all immortals. ":" is a synonym for immtalk. Using
this command with no argument toggles the immortal channel.

